data.description: Terrific views from this North Fork parcel and home! A beautiful curved sloped 2.5 acre parcel facing the West for gorgeous sunset views! Paved road access to this comfy 1,250 sq ft, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with attached 2 car garage. Also, a separate car port. Approximately 2 miles to North Fork. It also has a huge fenced yard that is perfect for kids or furry babies!
